База данных проекта (PostgreSQL)

Имя БД: loadtrain

Схема инициализации:
- backend/db/init.sql

Основные таблицы:

1) athletes
- id (PK)
- external_id (UNIQUE)
- full_name
- sex
- birth_date
- weight_category_points
- created_at, updated_at

2) observation_periods
- id (PK)
- athlete_id (FK -> athletes.id, ON DELETE CASCADE)
- weeks_count
- sessions_per_week
- start_date
- competition_date
- bench_press_points
- squat_points
- deadlift_points
- total_points
- sport_rank
- created_at, updated_at
- ограничение: start_date < competition_date

3) rest_baselines
- id (PK)
- period_id (FK -> observation_periods.id, ON DELETE CASCADE, UNIQUE)
- creatinine_points
- protein_points
- myoglobin_points
- ketones_points
- created_at, updated_at

4) training_sessions
- id (PK)
- period_id (FK -> observation_periods.id, ON DELETE CASCADE)
- week_no
- session_no
- v_points
- p_points
- r_points
- creatinine_points
- protein_points
- myoglobin_points
- ketones_points
- created_at, updated_at
- уникальность: UNIQUE(period_id, week_no, session_no)

Связи (кардинальность):
- athletes (1) -> (N) observation_periods
- observation_periods (1) -> (1) rest_baselines
- observation_periods (1) -> (N) training_sessions

Индексы:
- idx_observation_periods_athlete (athlete_id, start_date DESC)
- idx_training_sessions_period_week (period_id, week_no, session_no)
- idx_training_sessions_period_created (period_id, created_at DESC)

Как подключиться из терминала:
PGPASSWORD=loadtrain_pass psql -h localhost -p 5432 -U loadtrain_user -d loadtrain

Полезные команды psql:
\dt
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM athletes;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM observation_periods;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM rest_baselines;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM training_sessions;
\q
